Actions.Text: REFERRED TO HOUSING, CONSTRUCTION AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT

Title: Relates to not-for-profits' use of certain residential dwellings
Summary: Relates to not-for-profits' use of certain residential dwellings for individuals who are or were homeless or at risk of homelessness.
LawCode: Amd §5, Emerg Ten Prot Act of 1974
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the emergency tenant protection act of nineteen seventy-four, in relation to not-for-profits' use of certain residential dwellings
